<h3>CSIR award for S&amp;T Innovations for Rural Development for the year 2007</h3>
<p>Nimbkar Agricultural Research Institute (NARI), Phaltan, Maharastra was awarded the prestigious CSIR award for S&amp;T Innovations for Rural Development for the year 2007. Dr Chanda Nimbkar (one of the contributors of 'Lilavati's Daughters') leads the Animal Husbandry Division of NARI.</p>
